Use any type of citrus peel and candy it. It is very sweet and a great snack for the kids. Make marmalade, chutney, jam, and savory sauces using citrus peel. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d2/Use-Citrus-Fruit-Peels-in-the-Home-and-Garden-Step-7Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Citrus-Fruit-Peels-in-the-Home-and-Garden-Step-7Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d2/Use-Citrus-Fruit-Peels-in-the-Home-and-Garden-Step-7Bullet3.jpg/v4-760px-Use-Citrus-Fruit-Peels-in-the-Home-and-Garden-Step-7Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
